Glenn Hunter (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glenn_Hunter_(actor) 0 Glenn Hunter (September 26, 1894 – December 30, 1945) was a stage and silent film actor who gained popularity in the 1920s on the Broadway stage.
